Description: The rest on the flight into Egypt, the Virgin is seated holding the Christ Child, Joseph in the background holding a staff in left right hand, fruit in the right, after Procaccini. 1593 Engraving
Bibliographic references: Bartsch / Le Peintre graveur (XVIII.19.2) (copy in reverse)
Acquisition name: Bequeathed by: Sir Hans Sloane (with Philipe's oval blindstamp and initials HS)
